ammys-nominations-2025-check-out-the-full-list-of-nominations-here-3811039">获得格莱美提名的人</a>来说，这是标志性的一年。</p><p>她迅速跻身流行歌星的行列为她赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-antonoff">杰克·安东诺夫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的赞誉，他们最近联手表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swift-and-sabrina-carpenter-perform-espresso-together-at-eras-show-3806719">卡彭特热门歌曲《Espresso》的原声混搭，并</a>称赞她是“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-hails-sabrina-carpenter-as-the-pop-princess-of-our-dreams-3807987">我们梦想中的流行公主</a>” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taylor-swift-and-sabrina-carpenter-perform-espresso-together-at-eras-show-3806719">“Please Please Please”</a>和斯威夫特的跳马曲目“Is It Over Now?”摘自<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">《1989（泰勒版）》</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3819563" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3819563" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3819563" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1.jpg" alt="萨布丽娜·卡彭特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/sabrina-carpenter-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3819563" class="wp-caption-text">萨布丽娜·卡彭特。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>明年，她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>和